description: Beautifully  appointed, fully  renovated contemporary townhouse by architect/owner. No expense was spared in this gut renovated home. Private entrance with sintered stone flooring has direct access to private garage with Epoxy flooring, Elfa storage system shelving and 60amp hookup for future vehicle charging station. Second floor has 2 bedrooms with custom European wardrobes, Primary bedroom has ensuite spa style bathroom with steam shower and heated flooring.Upper floor features open style skylit  living room/kitchen with soaring ceiling. High end kitchen features custom cabinetry, built in pantry, large kitchen island with sintered stone countertops. Thermador appliances steam oven,  convection oven and beverage center. Private walk out terrace has gas hook up for barbecue and outdoor heater.
